description: Clip from "Sound of Redemption - The Frank Morgan Story". Laurie Pepper takes about the old misconception of west coast vs east coast jazz, and managing Art Pepper, his heroin addiction and serving time with Frank Morgan.
title: Laurie Pepper on West Coast Jazz, Art Pepper + Frank Morgan
